{"text_id":54996,"tokens":["#"," How"," to"," Help"," a"," Child"," With"," a"," Visual"," Im","pairment","\n\n","Supporting"," a"," child"," with"," a"," visual"," impairment"," can"," be"," a"," challenging"," yet"," rewarding"," experience","."," Visual"," impairments"," don","'","t"," define"," a"," child",";"," rather",","," they"," present"," unique"," opportunities"," for"," adaptation"," and"," learning","."," Here","'","s"," a"," comprehensive"," guide"," on"," supporting"," your"," child"," in"," various"," aspects"," of"," life",":","\n\n","##"," Control"," the"," lighting"," around"," the"," house",".","\n\n","Ensure"," the"," lighting"," is"," consistent"," and"," adequate"," but"," not"," overly"," bright","."," Soft"," lighting"," can"," reduce"," eye"," strain"," and"," make"," it"," easier"," for"," your"," child"," to"," navigate"," their"," environment","."," Adjust"," curtains"," and"," blinds"," to"," prevent"," harsh"," sunlight"," from"," creating"," difficult"," contrasts"," and"," shadows",".","\n\n","##"," Eliminate"," and"," remove"," hazards",".","\n\n","Inspect"," your"," living"," space"," for"," potential"," hazards"," like"," sharp"," objects",","," low"," furniture",","," or"," cords"," that"," could"," cause"," your"," child"," to"," trip","."," Secure"," or"," remove"," these"," items"," to"," create"," a"," safer"," environment","."," When"," re","decor","ating"," or"," moving"," items",","," inform"," your"," child"," about"," the"," changes"," to"," avoid"," confusion",".","\n\n","##"," Reduce"," glare",".","\n\n","G","lare"," from"," shiny"," surfaces"," can"," be"," distracting"," and"," uncomfortable","."," Use"," matte"," finishes"," on"," walls",","," floors",","," and"," furniture","."," Consider"," anti","-","g","lare"," coatings"," for"," screens"," and"," windows"," to"," make"," surfaces"," more"," comfortable"," for"," your"," child",".","\n\n","##"," Create"," color"," contrasts"," around"," the"," house",".","\n\n","High","-","contrast"," colors"," can"," help"," visually"," impaired"," children"," distinguish"," between"," objects"," and"," their"," surroundings","."," Use"," contrasting"," colors"," for"," walls"," and"," furniture",","," or"," bright"," tape"," on"," steps"," and"," door"," frames"," to"," alert"," your"," child"," to"," potential"," changes"," in"," the"," environment",".","\n\n","##"," Organize"," items"," properly",".","\n\n","Keeping"," items"," in"," consistent",","," designated"," places"," helps"," your"," child"," memorize"," their"," locations","."," Label"," shelves"," and"," drawers"," with"," bra","ille"," or"," tactile"," markings"," so"," your"," child"," can"," easily"," find"," what"," they","'","re"," looking"," for",".","\n\n","##"," Encourage"," texture"," and"," touch"," on"," items",".","\n\n","In","corporate"," different"," textures"," to"," help"," your"," child"," identify"," objects"," through"," touch","."," Use"," tactile"," markers"," or"," contrasting"," textures"," on"," commonly"," used"," items"," to"," aid"," recognition",".","\n\n","##"," Respond"," when"," your"," child"," makes"," sounds"," or"," noises",".","\n\n","Engage"," with"," your"," child"," whenever"," they"," attempt"," to"," communicate","."," Responding"," reinforces"," their"," efforts"," to"," interact"," and"," helps"," develop"," their"," communication"," skills",".","\n\n","##"," Play"," games"," that"," include"," sounds",","," songs",","," and"," taking"," turns",".","\n\n","In","corporate"," auditory"," elements"," into"," playtime","."," Games"," involving"," music",","," sound"," cues",","," and"," taking"," turns"," not"," only"," entertain"," but"," also"," improve"," auditory"," skills"," and"," social"," interaction",".","\n\n","##"," Offer"," your"," child"," opportunities"," to"," speak",".","\n\n","Encourage"," verbal"," expression"," by"," giving"," your"," child"," plenty"," of"," opportunities"," to"," speak","."," Engage"," them"," in"," conversations"," and"," ask"," open","-","ended"," questions"," to"," stimulate"," their"," thinking"," and"," language"," development",".","\n\n","##"," Make"," up"," planned"," mistakes",".","\n\n","Int","ention","ally"," make"," small",","," harmless"," mistakes"," in"," daily"," activities"," to"," encourage"," your"," child"," to"," identify"," and"," correct"," them","."," This"," helps"," boost"," their"," problem","-","solving"," skills"," and"," atten","tiveness",".","\n\n","##"," Communicate"," with"," your"," child"," daily",".","\n\n","Regular"," conversations"," build"," your"," child","\u2019","s"," language"," skills"," and"," confidence","."," Talk"," about"," their"," day",","," describe"," your"," surroundings",","," and"," involve"," them"," in"," decision","-","making"," processes",".","\n\n","##"," Allow"," your"," child"," to"," help"," out"," around"," the"," house",".","\n\n","Assign"," age","-","appropriate"," chores"," to"," foster"," independence"," and"," responsibility","."," Simple"," tasks"," like"," setting"," the"," table"," or"," folding"," laundry"," can"," boost"," their"," confidence"," and"," skills",".","\n\n","##"," Teach"," your"," child"," bra","ille",".","\n\n","Learning"," bra","ille"," is"," crucial"," for"," visually"," impaired"," children","."," Seek"," resources"," and"," professionals"," who"," can"," help"," your"," child"," become"," proficient"," in"," bra","ille"," reading"," and"," writing",".","\n\n","##"," Find"," tools"," to"," help"," make"," learning"," easier",".","\n\n","There"," are"," numerous"," assis","tive"," devices"," and"," tools",","," such"," as"," bra","ille"," readers",","," magn","ifiers",","," and"," screen"," readers",","," that"," can"," significantly"," enhance"," your"," child","'","s"," learning"," experience","."," Research"," and"," invest"," in"," the"," ones"," best"," suited"," for"," your"," child","\u2019","s"," needs",".","\n\n","##"," Do"," hands","-","on"," learning"," activities",".","\n\n","Engage"," your"," child"," in"," hands","-","on"," activities"," that"," encourage"," exploration"," and"," learning","."," This"," could"," include"," tactile"," art"," projects",","," interactive"," science"," experiments",","," or"," cooking"," together",".","\n\n","##"," Teach"," your"," child"," social"," skills",".","\n\n","Model"," and"," teach"," appropriate"," social"," interactions",","," like"," greeting"," others",","," taking"," turns",","," and"," expressing"," gratitude","."," Social"," stories"," and"," role","-","playing"," can"," also"," be"," effective"," tools",".","\n\n","##"," Demonstrate"," and"," teach"," your"," child"," good"," manners",".","\n\n","Good"," manners"," are"," essential"," for"," social"," interactions","."," Teach"," your"," child"," to"," use"," polite"," language",","," listen"," attentively",","," and"," show"," respect"," to"," others",".","\n\n","##"," Help"," your"," child"," learn"," about"," the"," world"," around"," them",".","\n\n","Provide"," diverse"," experiences"," to"," help"," your"," child"," understand"," their"," environment","."," Describe"," new"," places",","," introduce"," different"," sounds"," and"," smells",","," and"," explain"," how"," things"," work",".","\n\n","##"," Meet"," the"," Blind"," and"," Vis","ually"," Impaired"," community",".","\n\n","Connecting"," with"," others"," who"," share"," similar"," experiences"," can"," offer"," support"," and"," valuable"," insights","."," Participate"," in"," events"," and"," groups"," for"," the"," visually"," impaired"," community",".","\n\n","##"," Meet"," other"," families"," with"," blind"," or"," visually"," impaired"," children",".","\n\n","Building"," a"," network"," of"," families"," with"," similar"," experiences"," can"," provide"," emotional"," support",","," advice",","," and"," friendship"," for"," both"," you"," and"," your"," child",".","\n\n","##"," Find"," services"," for"," your"," child",".","\n\n","Explore"," availabl